/**
 * AI Coursebook Generator v9.1
 * Generates comprehensive training coursebooks with detailed HTML content
 *
 * v9.1 CHANGES (per user request):
 *   1. GPT Image 2 images are returned/embedded as base64 IMMEDIATELY — so backups never lose images.
 *   2. Every page is backed up to Google Drive AS SOON AS it is created (already done, now persistent).
 *   3. Job state is saved to Drive on EVERY task (not every 5) — Resume always works.
 *   4. `job.htmlParts` no longer accumulates base64 blobs in cache (which caused silent resume failure).
 *      Content lives only in Drive backup chunks; job state carries only progress metadata.
 *   5. Resume flow restores the live preview from Drive backups (images intact, URLs never expired).
 *
 * FEATURES KEPT: Resume, Pause, Dashboard, Employee list, Job persistence, Drive backup,
 *                Content Analysis image engine, Live editable preview, HTML download, PDF via print.
 */

